The People of the State of New York ex rel. George Mitchell, Appellant, v Robert Henderson, as Superintendent of the Auburn Correctional Facility, Respondent.

— Appeal unanimously dismissed as moot. (See People ex rel. Wilder v Markley, 26 NY2d 648.) (Appeal from judgment of Cayuga Supreme Court — article 78.) Present — Simons, J. P., Dillon, Hancock, Denman and Goldman, JJ.
